description:
Exclusive Fairy for the following TEN characters, available for unlimited use on all maps in the game:

-John Joe's Fairy Clothes
-Salonbus's Fairy Clothes
-Jintaro's Fairy Clothes
-Madam Chyan's Fairy Clothes
-Uncle Tuu's Fairy Clothes
-Candy's Fairy Clothes
-Wu Mhi's Fairy Clothes
-Daniel's Fairy Clothes
-Baby King's Fairy Clothes
-Princess Sarah's Fairy Clothes

*To use the Fairy Clothes Pack, you must own the 'Richman 4 Fun' (sold separately).
name: Fairy Clothes Pack
